
The following python modules should be installed:

On Ubuntu:

sudo easy_install python-daemon
sudo easy_install apscheduler
sudo apt-get install python-sqlalchemy


And everything from contrib/ folder.

If necessary, contrib/ modules can be installed "locally":

PyCCN:
	PYTHONARCHDIR='../../lib' ./waf configure
	./waf install

dnspython:
	./setup.py install --install-lib=../../lib

py-setproctitle
	python ./setup.py install --install-lib=../../lib

